nbsOtnpmCurrentBbe   OBJECT-TYPE
    SYNTAX          Counter64
    MAX-ACCESS      read-only
    STATUS          current
    DESCRIPTION
       "The number of Background Block Errors (BBE) so far,
        i.e. the count of Bit Interleave Parity (BIP8) errors."
